OL,3,CHow much should Guernsey's minimum
OL,4,Cwage increase by?
OL,6,FGuernsey politicians return from their
OL,7,Fsummer break today (Wednesday 4
OL,8,FSeptember) and among the topics up for
OL,9,Fdebate is the island's minimum wage.
OL,11,FDeputies are discussing how much it
OL,12,Fshould increase with the initial plan
OL,13,Fto raise it for adults from #10.65 to
OL,14,F#12 an hour.
OL,16,FHowever, some politicians argue this
OL,17,Fis too high and believe it would put
OL,18,Ftoo much pressure on employers,
OL,19,Fultimately leading to higher prices
OL,20,Ffor consumers amid ongoing cost of
OL,21,Fliving pressures.
