OL,3,CHow much should Guernsey's minimum
OL,4,Cwage increase by?
OL,6,FEven if the original rate is approved,
OL,7,FGuernsey's minimum salary will still
OL,8,Fbe #1 lower per hour than Jersey from
OL,9,FApril 2025 when their uplift takes
OL,10,Feffect.
OL,12,FAny changes will take effect from 1
OL,13,FOctober 2024.
